<pb n="1115b" id="T12.0393.1115b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1115b01"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"></milestone>
<lb n="1115b02"/><head type="no">No. 393</head>
<lb n="1115b03"/><div1 type="jing"><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"></mulu><jhead><title><note n="1115014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛說）＋迦【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="1115014"><lem>迦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">佛說迦</rdg></app>葉赴佛<note n="1115015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔般〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="1115015"><lem>般</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>涅槃經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="1115b04"/>
<lb n="1115b05"/><byline type="Translator">東晉<note n="1115016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔西域沙門〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔西域沙門〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115016"><lem>西域沙門</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>竺曇無蘭譯</byline>
<lb n="1115b06"/><p>昔佛在世時。摩訶迦葉。於諸比丘中。最長年
<lb n="1115b07"/>高才明智慧。其身亦有金色相好。佛每說法。
<lb n="1115b08"/>常與其對坐。人民見之或呼為佛師。於是迦
<lb n="1115b09"/>葉乃辭佛到伊<note n="1115017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">篩梨＝蒢黎【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">篩梨＝蒢黎【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115017"><lem>篩梨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">蒢黎</rdg></app>山中。一山名普能。周旋
<lb n="1115b10"/>數千里。去舍衛國二萬六千里。多出七寶。甘
<lb n="1115b11"/>果不<note n="1115018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訾＝貲【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訾＝貲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115018"><lem>訾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">貲</rdg></app>。名香好藥栴檀三種。其一種芳香。一
<lb n="1115b12"/>種治人百病。一種可用染五色。眾香雜藥不
<lb n="1115b13"/>可稱數。亦有走翔鳥獸師子<note n="1115019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">虎＝&CB00333;【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">虎＝&CB00333;【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115019"><lem>虎</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&CB00333;</rdg></app>狼白象騏驎
<lb n="1115b14"/>朱<note n="1115020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">雀＝鳥【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">雀＝鳥【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115020"><lem>雀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">鳥</rdg></app>鳳凰。或有清淨異學道士。時有方石平
<lb n="1115b15"/>正。其色如琉璃。縱廣百二十里。奇樹蔭涼華
<lb n="1115b16"/>葉五色。冬夏茂盛列生石上。迦葉前後教授
<lb n="1115b17"/><note n="1115021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝一【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二＝一【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115021"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">一</rdg></app>千弟子。皆清淨高行得羅漢者。常坐此石
<lb n="1115b18"/><note n="1115022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔上〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔上〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115022"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。誦經行道。又有清淨甘<note n="1115023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">香＝果【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">香＝果【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115023"><lem>香</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">果</rdg></app>泉水。周旋
<lb n="1115b19"/><note n="1115024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">四＝三【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">四＝三【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115024"><lem>四</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">三</rdg></app>十里。其<note n="1115025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">水中則有優曇華＝側生優曇華青蓮華【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">水中則有優曇華＝側生優曇華青蓮華【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115025"><lem>水中則有優曇華</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">側生優曇華青蓮華</rdg></app>。紺色華紅色
<lb n="1115b20"/>華紫色華。迦葉弟子七人同夕得夢。其一比
<lb n="1115b21"/>丘。夢見<note n="1115026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔其〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔其〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115026"><lem>其</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>所坐方石中央分破樹皆根拔。復
<lb n="1115b22"/>一比丘夢見四十里泉水皆乾竭華悉零落。一
<lb n="1115b23"/>比丘夢見拘羅邊坐皆傾毀。一比丘夢<note n="1115027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔見〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔見〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115027"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>閻
<lb n="1115b24"/>浮利地皆傾陷。一比丘夢見須彌山崩。一比
<lb n="1115b25"/>丘夢見金輪王薨。一比丘夢見日月墮地天
<lb n="1115b26"/>下失明。晨起各以所夢啟迦葉。迦葉告言。我
<lb n="1115b27"/>曹前見光明地時大動。卿等復得是夢。佛將
<lb n="1115b28"/>般泥洹。即&CB00330;諸弟子往赴俱夷那竭國。道見
<lb n="1115b29"/><note n="1115028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115028"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>婆羅門。持文陀羅華。迦葉即問言。卿從
<pb n="1115c" id="T12.0393.1115c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1115c01"/>何來。欲何所至。那得是天華。答言。我從<note n="1115029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔俱夷〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔俱夷〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115029"><lem>俱
<lb n="1115c02"/>夷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>那竭國來。時佛<note n="1115030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔般〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="1115030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔般〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="1115030"><lem>般</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>泥洹已經七日諸天往
<lb n="1115c03"/>赴。悉持天華天香供養佛身。此華即是。迦葉
<lb n="1115c04"/>聞是語。便自投於地啼泣而言。佛今般泥洹。
<lb n="1115c05"/>三界失明。將復何依恃。<note n="1115031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便帥＝彼師【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便帥＝彼師【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115031"><lem>便帥</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">彼師</rdg></app>將諸弟子進
<lb n="1115c06"/>道。未到數百里。便見四天王及梵釋諸天。皆
<lb n="1115c07"/>持七寶蓋名香好華。悉<note n="1115032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔往供…諸天〕六字－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔往供…諸天〕六字－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115032" word-count="6"><lem>往供養佛。諸天</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>作
<lb n="1115c08"/>十二部音樂。亦有阿須輪王諸大鬼神側塞
<lb n="1115c09"/>空中。又<note n="1115033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＝具【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見＝具【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115033"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">具</rdg></app>俱夷那竭國王。及諸&CB00444;國王。各
<lb n="1115c10"/>從其群僚數百萬人。見迦葉將諸弟子到。是
<lb n="1115c11"/>時國貴末羅<note n="1115034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔弗〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔弗〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115034"><lem>弗</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>王。則&CB00330;國人民皆令避道。使
<lb n="1115c12"/>迦葉及<note n="1115035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔諸〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔諸〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115035"><lem>諸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>弟子得進。阿那律出迎相見言。佛
<lb n="1115c13"/>般泥洹已<note n="1115036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">七＝士【宋】</note><app n="1115036"><lem>七</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">士</rdg></app>日。耶維火不然。但待賢者到
<lb n="1115c14"/><note n="1115037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔耳〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔耳〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115037"><lem>耳</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。阿難見迦葉。便自<note n="1115038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">投＋（此）【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">投＋（此）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115038"><lem>投</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">投此</rdg></app>地啼哭不自勝。有
<lb n="1115c15"/>一老比丘名波或。即止阿難言。止止。佛在時
<lb n="1115c16"/>常禁制我等不得自由。佛今<app type="＊" source="1115030"><lem>般</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>泥洹。吾等得
<lb n="1115c17"/>自在。莫復啼哭。時有天聞波或語。即舉手搏
<lb n="1115c18"/>之。迦葉便前接持天止之。謂波或言。佛今般
<lb n="1115c19"/>泥洹。一切失所<note n="1115039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">恃＝持【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1115039"><lem>恃</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">持</rdg></app>。汝獨愚癡而反喜快。波
<lb n="1115c20"/>或聞是語<note n="1115040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意解＝竟【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">意解＝竟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115040"><lem>意解</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">竟</rdg></app>即得阿羅漢<note n="1115041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔道〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔道〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115041"><lem>道</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。迦葉便與
<lb n="1115c21"/><note n="1115042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸弟子＝弟子俱【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸弟子＝弟子俱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115042"><lem>諸弟子</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">弟子俱</rdg></app>頭面著地。作禮繞棺三匝<note n="1115043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔悲哀〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔悲哀〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115043"><lem>悲哀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>而
<lb n="1115c22"/>言。我等今日不知佛頭足所在。<note n="1115044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（佛威…佛言））二十七字＝（（即便悲哀而說偈言））八字【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（（佛威…佛言））二十七字＝（（即便悲哀而說偈言））八字【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115044" word-count="27"><lem>佛威神則為
<lb n="1115c23"/>出足。諸天人民莫不感傷。於是摩訶迦葉乃
<lb n="1115c24"/>說偈讚佛言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">即便悲哀而說偈言</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="1115c25"/><lg><l>佛為三界乘</l><l>度於生死淵</l>
<lb n="1115c26"/><l><note n="1115045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">澹泊＝憺怕【三】【宮】</note><note n="1115045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">澹泊＝憺怕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1115045"><lem>澹泊</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">憺怕</rdg></app>昇泥洹</l><l>微妙越世間</l>
<pb n="1116a" id="T12.0393.1116a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1116a01"/><l>佛為無量明</l><l>照於愚癡冥</l>
<lb n="1116a02"/><l>願為一切人</l><l>顯耀<note n="1116001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">現＝見【三】【宮】</note><note n="1116001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">現＝見【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1116001"><lem>現</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">見</rdg></app>威靈</l>
<lb n="1116a03"/><l>佛為大慈哀</l><l>所度無央數</l>
<lb n="1116a04"/><l>尊體處金棺</l><l>清淨寂然安</l>
<lb n="1116a05"/><l>願用優和德</l><l>見身色相光</l>
<lb n="1116a06"/><l>普令天及人</l><l>興起無量福</l>
<lb n="1116a07"/><l>佛為開現法</l><l>眾生受潤澤</l>
<lb n="1116a08"/><l>得止生死輪</l><l><note n="1116002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或＝惑【三】【宮】</note><note n="1116002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">或＝惑【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1116002"><lem>或</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">惑</rdg></app>者入正諦</l>
<lb n="1116a09"/><l>已蒙如來恩</l><l>頭面禮佛足</l>
<lb n="1116a10"/><l>今但&CB00418;<note n="1116003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">金棺＝棺槨【三】【宮】</note><note n="1116003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">金棺＝棺槨【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1116003"><lem>金棺</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">棺槨</rdg></app></l><l>心為悲感傷</l>
<lb n="1116a11"/><l>佛雖就無為</l><l>聖達靡不實</l>
<lb n="1116a12"/><l>見後有疑<note n="1116004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諦＝諍【三】【宮】</note><note n="1116004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諦＝諍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1116004"><lem>諦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">諍</rdg></app></l><l>出足於金棺</l>
<lb n="1116a13"/><l>起分是生死</l><l>佛以不復愁</l>
<lb n="1116a14"/><l>法身慧常存</l><l>莫呼永泥洹</l></lg>
<lb n="1116a15"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><title>迦葉赴佛<note n="1116005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔般〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="1116005"><lem>般</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>涅槃經</title></jhead></juan></div1>
